        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Disclosing Aid Spent to Ensure Relief Act of 2021 or the DISASTER Act of 2021 </b></p> <p>This bill requires the Office of Management and Budget to submit an annual report to Congress on all disaster-related assistance provided by the federal government. The report must include all federal obligations related to disaster response, recovery, mitigation efforts, and administrative costs associated with these activities for specified agencies and programs. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
